" data-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21589" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21589">Do I need to have an applicant account on SchoolSpring to =
apply for positions?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21589">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21589"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21590" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Yes, an applicant account is required to be able to apply for positio=
ns via SchoolSpring.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21591" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21591" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21591">How do I create an applicant account on SchoolSpring?</a><=
/h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21591">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21591"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21592" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>To create an applicant account click '<strong>Sign In/Register'&nbsp;=
</strong>at the top right of the page.&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<figure class=3D"fsImage"><picture><img alt=3D"SignIn-Register" data-image-=
