	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21593" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21593" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21593">How frequently are jobs posted?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21593">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21593"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21594" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Jobs are posted as they become available.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21595" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21595" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21595">I do not have a computer or internet connection at home. C=
an I submit a paper application?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21595">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21595"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21596" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>No. ALL employment applications must be submitted via the online appl=
ication system. You may also access the online application process via the =
internet at a local public library or the NE Department of Employment &amp;=
 Workforce.&nbsp;</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21597" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21597" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21597">How do I obtain an email address?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21597">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21597"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21598" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>An email address is required of all applicants. If you do not have an=
 email address, you must create one prior to applying. There are several fr=
ee email providers such as Yahoo, MSN Hotmail and Gmail.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21599" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21599" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21599">How do I find out what jobs are currently available?</a></=
h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21599">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21599"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21600" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>View&nbsp;<a aria-label=3D"Current Job Openings - Opens a new window"=
 href=3D"https://omaha.tedk12.com/hire/index.aspx" rel=3D"noopener noreferr=
er" target=3D"_blank">Current Job Openings</a>&nbsp;and enter basic search =
criteria into the "Search Jobs" field. Applicable job postings will be disp=
layed, and you can select posting titles to review.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21601" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21601" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21601">What if I have forgotten my password?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21601">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21601"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21602" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>On the PowerSchool splash screen, you can put in the email you used a=
nd then click "Continue". You can then select "Forgot your password?" and i=
t will send a reset link to the email address you used. Be sure to check yo=
ur junk and spam folders. If you are not receiving an email or are having t=
rouble, please call the Applicant Support Line at 877-974-7437 and they wil=
l be able to assist.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>




	</div>


	</div>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsLayout fsOneColumnLayout fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D=
"fsEl_21603" data-use-new=3D"true">

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<div class=3D" fsDiv fsStyleColumn fsStyleColumn-1 fsStyleColumn-last fs=
StyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21604">

				<section class=3D"fsElement fsContent card primary" id=3D"fsEl_21605" d=
ata-use-new=3D"true">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle">E-Verify &amp; EEO</h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>The Omaha Public School District participates in the E-Verify Program=
. E-Verify is an internet-based system that allows employers to determine t=
he eligibility of their employees to work in the United States.&nbsp;E-Veri=
fy=C2=AE is a registered trademark of the U.S. Department of Homeland Secur=
it</p>

<h3>E-Verify Links</h3>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a aria-label=3D"E-Verify Participation Poster English and Spanish - Op=
ens a new window" data-ally-content-id=3D"e77a664f-46af-4777-bf81-893c8658f=
38f" data-ally-file-eid=3D"13669" data-file-name=3D"E-Verify_Participation_=
Poster_ES.pdf" data-resource-uuid=3D"e23ebb2d-9bee-4bbc-a48b-d2a9aa39982a" =
href=3D"https://www.ops.org/fs/resource-manager/view/e23ebb2d-9bee-4bbc-a48=
b-d2a9aa39982a" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">E-Verify Part=
icipation Poster English and Spanish</a></p>
	</li>
	<li><a aria-label=3D"E-Verify Right to Work Poster English - Opens a new w=
indow" data-ally-content-id=3D"94693fa7-49d5-4319-bd2b-0dae6fa29052" data-a=
lly-file-eid=3D"13670" data-file-name=3D"IER_RighttoWorkPoster.pdf" data-re=
source-uuid=3D"be7ecc02-a003-4430-a864-ad1386d651fc" href=3D"https://www.op=
s.org/fs/resource-manager/view/be7ecc02-a003-4430-a864-ad1386d651fc" rel=3D=
"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">E-Verify Right to Work Poster Engli=
sh</a></li>
	<li><a aria-label=3D"E-Verify Right to Work Poster Espanol - Opens a new w=
indow" data-ally-content-id=3D"19e9f9ec-2adb-4e34-9bc8-a8fbc5365c91" data-a=
lly-file-eid=3D"13671" data-file-name=3D"IER_RighttoWorkPosterES.pdf" data-=
resource-uuid=3D"33620996-f6f1-4627-baba-728f107db642" href=3D"https://www.=
ops.org/fs/resource-manager/view/33620996-f6f1-4627-baba-728f107db642" rel=
=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">E-Verify Right to Work Poster Es=
panol</a></li>
</ul>

<h3>EEO&nbsp;Links</h3>

<p>Applicants have rights under Federal &amp; State Employment Laws</p>

<ul>
	<li><a aria-label=3D"Federal Employee Rights - Opens a new window" href=3D=
"https://www.nebraska.gov/employment/employee-rights/" rel=3D"noopener nore=
ferrer" target=3D"_blank">Federal Employee Rights</a></li>
	<li><a aria-invalid=3D"true" aria-label=3D"State of Nebraska Employee Righ=
ts - Opens a new window" href=3D"https://www.nebraska.gov/employment/employ=
ee-rights/" rel=3D"noopener" target=3D"_blank">State of Nebraska Employee R=
ights</a></li>
	<li><a aria-invalid=3D"true" aria-label=3D"Federal Occupational Safety and=
 Health Administration (OSHA) - Opens a new window" href=3D"https://www.osh=
a.gov/" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">Federal Occupational =
Safety and Health Administration (OSHA)</a></li>
	<li><a aria-label=3D"Federal Equal Employment Opportunity Commission (EEO)=
 - Opens a new window" href=3D"https://www.eeoc.gov/" rel=3D"noopener noref=
errer" target=3D"_blank">Federal Equal Employment Opportunity Commission (E=
EO)</a></li>
	<li><a aria-label=3D"Federal Uniformed Services Employment and Reemploymen=
t Rights Act (USERRA) - Opens a new window" href=3D"https://www.dol.gov/age=
ncies/vets/programs/userra" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" target=3D"_blank">F=
ederal Uniformed Services Employment and Reemployment Rights Act (USERRA)</=
a></li>
</ul>


