				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21616" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21616">How do I see my submitted applications on SchoolSpring?</a=
></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21616">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21616"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21617" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>You&nbsp;can&nbsp;view any applications submitted with Omaha Public S=
chools by navigating to&nbsp;'<strong>My Jobs'</strong>&nbsp;&gt; '<strong>=
Submitted Applications</strong>'.&nbsp;</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21618" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21618" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21618">Can I apply for more than one job at a time?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21618">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21618"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21619" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Yes. Select the job of interest and click the "Apply for this job!" b=
utton.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21620" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21620" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21620">Must I fill out all sections of the online application?</a=
></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21620">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21620"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21621" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Yes. Fill out all pertinent sections of the online application.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21622" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21622" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21622">What do you consider a "complete" application?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21622">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21622"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21623" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>A completed application must include valid email addresses for refere=
nces.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21624" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21624" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21624">How long does my application remain active?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21624">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21624"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21625" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Your application remains active for two years from the date of your a=
pplication.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21626" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21626" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21626">What happens to my application after I submit it?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21626">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21626"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21627" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>After you have electronically submitted your application, you will re=
ceive an email confirming the submission. All applications are then reviewe=
d and screened against position qualifications and references are verified.=
 Candidates who best meet the position requirements will be contacted by Hu=
man Resources to schedule an interview. All applications are retained for a=
 two-year period.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21628" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21628" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21628">Can I add or remove documents in my SchoolSpring profile?<=
/a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21628">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21628"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21629" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Yes, under 'My Profile' within SchoolSpring.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21630" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21630" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21630">Can I update an application once it has been submitted?</a=
></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21630">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21630"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21631" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>No, you cannot make changes after you submit your application.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21632" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21632" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21632">Do I have to re-enter my information every time I apply?</=
a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21632">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21632"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21633" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>No, if you use the SAME email and password each time, your profile in=
formation will populate.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21634" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21634" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21634">If I apply multiple times for the same job, which applicat=
ion do you look at?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21634">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21634"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21635" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Upon applying for a specific job posting, you are no longer able to s=
ubmit an application for that position again.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21636" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21636" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21636">What format does my resume, cover letter and any other doc=
uments need to be in?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21636">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21636"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21637" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Any document you upload to the site can be in the following formats:<=
/p>

<ul>
	<li>PDF (pdf) - Highly recommended!</li>
	<li>MS Word document (doc or docx)</li>
	<li>MS Works document (wps)</li>
	<li>Plain text format (txt)</li>
	<li>Rich text format (rtf)</li>
</ul>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21638" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21638" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21638">How should I supply my references?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21638">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21638"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21639" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Three complete references are required. Enter reference information (=
name, phone number and email address) for each of your references in the se=
ction called References.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21640" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21640" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21640">What is the expected turnaround time and method of contact=
?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21640">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21640"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21641" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>Once your application is submitted, you will receive an email notific=
ation from the system that you have successfully submitted your application=
. Turnaround time depends on the application and the nature of the position=
 you are applying for.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>
	<section class=3D"fsElement fsPanel fsStyleAutoclear" id=3D"fsEl_21642" da=
ta-use-new=3D"true" role=3D"tabpanel">

				<header>
				<h2 class=3D"fsElementTitle"><a role=3D"button" aria-controls=3D"fsPane=
lContent_21642" aria-expanded=3D"false" href=3D"https://www.ops.org/careers=
#fs-panel-21642">Will I be contacted for a job interview?</a></h2>
	</header>
	<div class=3D"fsElementContent" aria-hidden=3D"true" id=3D"fsPanelContent_=
21642">
		<a id=3D"fs-panel-21642"></a>
	<div class=3D"fsElement fsContent" id=3D"fsEl_21643" data-use-new=3D"true"=
>

				<div class=3D"fsElementContent">
			<p>All applications are reviewed and screened. Those applicants meeting =
the specific criteria for job openings are contacted.</p>


	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>




	</div>


	</div>



	</div>


	</section>




	</div>


	</section>




	</div>





	</div>
